snippet.title: Kiwi Khaos MSX Jam build
snippet.description: Here's a short video from the Retro Platform Jam build of Kiwi Khaos. It's a short little MSX1 game made by me and a friend. Currently it could use some bugfixing and numerous upgrades are planned, including a ZX Spectrum port, but it certainly was fun to make.
